profile:
For every Home Maintenance need that may arise, Handyman Connection of Kelowna is committed to providing you with dependable and skilled Handymen, great customer service, and first class workmanship. Just one call or click brings our expertise right to your door. Handyman Connection of Kelowna can help turn your "to-do" list into "done."

Home repairs, renovations and remodeling are what we get excited about. Handyman Connection Kelowna is your single solution for that list of home maintenance and home improvement that seems to grow longer every day. Whether you need something installed, built, fixed or maintained, we are your reliable and trusted partner for all your home repair, renovating and remodeling needs. Your home needs expertise and we have the experts at Handyman Connection of Kelowna.
services:
Small to medium home repairs and renovations
•	Carpentry services
•	Tile & flooring*
•	Drywall install, patch or replace
•	Deck repair & building
•	Fence repair & building
•	General home maintenance
•	Painting and wall treatments
•	Home shelving & Storage
•	Plumbing services*
•	Electrical services*
•	Bathroom remodeling
•	Basement remodeling
•	Kitchen remodeling


*subcontracted to licensed trades
warranty_terms: 1 year written guarantee on all labour. (90 days on plumbing)

profile:
I offer a professional home repair service for handyman prices. Small jobs are my specialty. My professional handyman services and great prices have been keeping my customers happy for over 30 years. $40/hr. 
Services include:Installations, plumbing, electronics work, deck repairs, carpentry, drywall patching, and painting. You name it, I will fix it. My dependable handyman services are also available to commercial clients. I am a true jack-of-all-trades and I hold certificates in a variety of fields, including electronics, computers, and plastic welding. Bonded & Insured 
What is important is not the money I make
But the smiles I create
Prefer calls 250-215-3576 anytime or fossilized@live.ca
